### Connectivity categories

  1. Impeded (0 - 0.7)
  2. Diffuse (0.7 - 1.3)
  3. Intensified (1.3 - 1.7)
  4. Channelized (1.7 - 9999)



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
m <- c(0, 0.7, 1,
       0.7, 1.3, 2,
       1.4, 1.7, 3,
       1.7, 9999, 4)
rclmat <- matrix(m, ncol=3, byrow=TRUE)
r4a = as.factor(classify(r3a, rclmat, include.lowest=TRUE))
r4b = as.factor(classify(r3b, rclmat, include.lowest=TRUE))
r4c = as.factor(classify(r3c, rclmat, include.lowest=TRUE))
r4d = as.factor(classify(r3d, rclmat, include.lowest=TRUE))
```
:::



::: {.panel-tabset}

